title: Savage Dragon #153 (w/Image United Prelude part 1)
description:
By: Erik Larsen

'FAMILY REUNION'
Savage Dragon is reunited with his son Malcolm but the reunion is anything but happy. What's a son to do when his father has merged with a ruthless, unyielding killer? Meanwhile Dart continues to manipulate the Original Daredevil and the mysterious new Overlord is making a few changes to the Vicious Circle in his quest for power! PLUS: IMAGE UNITED STARTS HERE, IN PART ONE OF A SPECIAL FOUR-PART PRELUDE STORY BY ROBERT KIRKMAN & WHILCE PORTACIO!
